## 🎯 Why Narrow Scope Makes Us Stronger

### The Trap (Avoid This)
```
We explain: S₈ + Lyman-α + JWST + H₀ + dark matter + ...

Result: We claim to fix everything
         → Nobody believes us
         → Each domain has specialists who reject us
         → We explain nothing well
```

### The Strategy (What We Do)
```
We explain: S₈ and Lyman-α specifically

Result: We have two clear, testable predictions
        → Easy to falsify (good!)
        → Other domains can use our mechanism if it works
        → We're the experts on structure formation, not everything
        → Specialists respect focused science
```

